<template>
    <v-form v-model="valid">
    <v-container>
      <v-row>
        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="nome_empresa"
            :rules="nameRules"
            :counter="10"
            label="Nome Empresa"
            required
            hide-details
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="email"
            :rules="emailRules"
            label="E-mail"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="cnpj"
            :rules="nameRules"
            :counter="14"
            label="CNPJ"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>

      <v-row>
        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="cep"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="CEP"
            required
            hide-details
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="endereco"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Endereço"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="numero"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Número"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>

      <v-row>
        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="complemento"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Complemento"
            required
            hide-details
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="bairro"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Bairro"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="cidade"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Cidade"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>

      <v-row>
        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="estado"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Estado"
            required
            hide-details
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="telefone"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="Telefone"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>

        <v-col
          cols="12"
          md="4"
        >
          <v-text-field
            v-model="atuacao"
            :rules="nameRules"
            label="atuacao"
            hide-details
            required
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-btn
        class="me-4"
        @click="v$.$validate"
        >
        submit
        </v-btn>
        <v-btn @click="clear">
        clear
        </v-btn>
    </v-container>
  </v-form>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    data: () => ({
      valid: false,
      nome_empresa: '',
      cnpj: '',
      email: '',
      cep: '',
      endereco: '',
      numero: '',
      complemento: '',
      bairro: '',
      cidade: '',
      estado: '',
      telefone: '',
      atuacao: '',

      nameRules: [
        value => {
          if (value) return true

          return 'Nome é obrigatório.'
        },
        value => {
          if (value?.length <= 10) return true

          return 'Nome não pode ter mais de 10 letras.'
        },
      ],
      email: '',
      emailRules: [
        value => {
          if (value) return true

          return 'E-mail é obrigatório.'
        },
        value => {
          if (/.+@.+\..+/.test(value)) return true

          return 'E-mail inválido.'
        },
      ],
    }),
  }
</script>
